    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, offering razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue with an immaculate interior, this vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard with all fluid intervals strictly followed. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
