      "description": "This 2019 BMW M4 is a true collector-grade specimen, maintained with obsessive attention to detail. Finished in a stunning San Marino Blue, the exterior is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. There are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the Silverstone Merino leather remains in showroom condition\u2014firm bolsters, no creasing, and that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full dealership service history and only 12,000 miles on the odometer. Every button, switch, and feature operates as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new performance icon.",
