      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2005 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to produce a high-revving 333 hp. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. Critically, the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been proactively addressed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014eliminating the common failure points of this chassis. The suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and factory-spec damping. The exterior retains its deep luster with original paint thickness, while the interior Nappa leather shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, analog masterpiece for the purist collector.",
